<p>Maybe my critics are right in calling me an ugly troll. But I&#8217;m not the villain in this story. <a href="http://maybemaimed.com/2010/04/02/stand-against-stigma/" rel="nofollow">I&#8217;m just also not the hero</a>.</p>
